ms and homesteaders, with bagged pickup and bulk delivery options that make sense for your operation.</p><div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 pt-4"><a href="/order-feed" class="inline-block px-6 py-3 bg-[var(--bronze)] text-white font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-wide rounded hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity">Order Feed</a><a href="#how-it-works" class="inline-block px-6 py-3 border-2 border-white text-white font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-wide rounded hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors">Learn More</a></div></div></section></div></section><section class="py-12 md:py-16 border-y border-[var(--ink-soft)]"><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8"><div><p class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[var(--bronze)]">Local</p><p class="text-[var(--ink-muted)] mt-2">Serving small farms and homesteaders throughout Missouri with reliable feed and honest service.</p></div><div><p class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[var(--bronze)]">Transparent</p><p class="text-[var(--ink-muted)] mt-2">Non-GMO, quality-focused blends sourced and mixed with care for your animals&#x27; health.</p></div><div><p class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[var(--bronze)]">Practical</p><p class="text-[var(--ink-muted)] mt-2">Whether you need eight bags or eight tons, we offer flexible ordering and delivery that works for you.</p></div></div></section><section class="py-12 md:py-16"><h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-[var(--ink)]">The Frustration</h2><p class="text-lg text-[var(--ink-muted)] mb-8 max-w-2xl">Small farm owners and homesteaders know the struggle:</p><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6"><div class="flex gap-4"><div class="text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--bronze)] flex-shrink-0">•</div><p class="text-[var(--ink-muted)]">Feed is too expensive at big-box retailers.</p></div><div class="flex gap-4"><div class="text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--bronze)] flex-shrink-0">•</div><p class="text-[var(--ink-muted)]">The nearest quality supplier is too far away.</p></div><div class="flex gap-4"><div class="text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--bronze)] flex-shrink-0">•</div><p class="text-[var(--ink-muted)]">Shipping costs eat up your savings.</p></div><div class="flex gap-4"><div class="text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--bronze)] flex-shrink-0">•</div><p class="text-[var(--ink-muted)]">Local options don&#x27;t carry what your animals need.</p></div><div class="flex gap-4"><div class="text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--bronze)] flex-shrink-0">•</div><p class="text-[var(--ink-muted)]">Your animals aren&#x27;t thriving on available feeds.</p></div></div></section><section id="how-it-works" class="py-12 md:py-16 bg-[var(--lace)] -mx-5 md:-mx-10 px-5 md:px-10 rounded"><h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-12 text-[var(--ink)]">Our Solution</h2><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12"><div><h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-[var(--bronze)]">Bagged Pickup</h3><p class="text-[var(--ink-muted)] leading-relaxed">No shipping. No middleman markup. Pick up pre-bagged feed on your schedule from our location in Marshall, Missouri. Perfect for smaller operations that need consistent supply without the hassle.</p><ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-[var(--ink-muted)]"><li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-[var(--bronze)] font-bold">➔</span><span>Convenient pickup times</span></li><li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-[var(--bronze)] font-bold">➔</span><span>No shipping cost</span></li><li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-[var(--bronze)] font-bold">➔</span><span>Exact quantities you need</span></li></ul></div><div><h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-[var(--bronze)]">Bulk Delivery</h3><p class="text-[var(--ink-muted)] leading-relaxed">Need a larger quantity? We deliver bulk feed directly to your farm. One trip to your property, one invoice, and your feed is where you need it. Affordable and efficient for growing operations.</p><ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-[var(--ink-muted)]"><li class="flex gap-2"><