 grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8"><div><h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Quality You Can Trust</h3><p class="text-blue-100">Non-GMO, freshly mixed, and formulated for the animals you&#x27;re raising. No shortcuts.</p></div><div><h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Real Relationships</h3><p class="text-blue-100">We&#x27;re not a corporate call center. Remi knows the challenges of small-farm feeding. You&#x27;ll get straightforward advice.</p></div><div><h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Local Support</h3><p class="text-blue-100">Based in Marshall, Missouri. Close to you. Quick to respond. Invested in your farm&#x27;s success.</p></div><div><h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Flexible Options</h3><p class="text-blue-100">Whether you need eight bags or eight tons, we scale to your needs without pressure or minimum orders.</p></div></div></section><section class="py-12 md:py-16"><div class="text-center"><h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6 text-[var(--ink)]">Ready to Order?</h2><p class="text-lg text-[var(--ink-muted)] mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Choose bagged pickup or bulk delivery, place your order, and let us help your farm thrive with feed you can trust.</p><div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center"><a href="/order-feed" class="px-8 py-3 bg-[var(--bronze)] text-white font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-wide rounded hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity">Place Your Order</a><a href="/contact" class="px-8 py-3 border-2 border-[var(--bronze)] text-[var(--bronze)] font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-wide rounded hover:bg-[var(--lace)] transition-colors">Get in Touch</a></div></div></section></main><footer class="bg-[var(--ink)] text-white mt-16"><div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-[90rem] px-5 md:px-10 py-12"><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-8"><div><h4 class="font-bold mb-3">Kesten Feed Co</h4><p class="text-blue-200 text-sm">High-quality non-GMO feed for Missouri farms and homesteaders.</p></div><div><h4 class="font-bold mb-3">C